	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: SEGA 32X NSF player</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The 32X takes in the Genesis' analogue RGB and overlays its own RGB &amp; encodes it.  The resulting output is still pretty clean as far as RGB goes, and since the video encoder in the 32X is superior to the Genesis', the combined video will look superior in composite as well.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


